  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The Web3 Provider dialog is very hard to use. Here are some suggestions for improving the user experience:\r\n\r\n- The initial confirmation prompt should be removed. The prompt for the URL already allows canceling the node connection.\r\n- The default URL should be `http://127.0.0.1:8545`. This URL also works on https pages (the notification about switching to 'http' can be removed as well!).\r\n- When the connection doesn't work, the dialog should show the error message, but keep the dialog open. This way typos in the URL input box can be fixed.\r\n",
